# readme-tos-file
Terms of Service for Server Saver Discord Bot

By using the Server Saver Discord Bot, you agree to be bound by the following terms and conditions Terms of Service. Please read them carefully before using the Bot.

1. Use of the Bot

 The Bot is intended solely for the purpose of assisting with moderation tasks within Discord servers.

 You agree to use the Bot in compliance with Discord's Terms of Service (https://discord.com/terms) and Community Guidelines (https://discord.com/guidelines).

2. Moderation Responsibilities

 While the Bot provides assistance with moderation tasks, ultimate responsibility for managing and enforcing server rules lies with the server administrators and moderators.

 The Bot creator(s) shall not be held liable for any actions taken by the Bot or its users in violation of server rules or Discord's Terms of Service.

3. Data Collection and Privacy

 The Bot may collect and store user data, including but not limited to messages, user IDs, and server activity logs, solely for the purpose of providing moderation services.

 We are committed to protecting the privacy and security of user data. Please refer to our Privacy Policy (link to privacy policy) for details on how we collect, use, and protect your data.

4. Limitation of Liability

 In no event shall slapeo (developer), nor its directors, employees, partners, agents, suppliers, or affiliates, be liable for any damages arising out of the use or inability to use the Bot, including but not limited to loss of data, profits, or business interruption.

 The Bot is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind, express or implied. We do not guarantee that the Bot will be error-free, secure, or meet your requirements.

5. Changes to Terms

 We reserve the right to modify or replace these Terms of Service at any time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting on our website or within the Bot. Your continued use of the Bot after any such changes constitutes your acceptance of the new Terms.

6. Contact Us

 If you have any questions or concerns about these Terms of Service, please contact us at slapeo1@serversaver.info.

By using the Bot, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by these Terms of Service.
